FILE- In this Oct. 8, 2015, file photo, Natalie Morales arrives at the Latin American Music Awards at the Dolby Theatre in Los Angeles.
NBC "Today" show anchor Morales is moving West to become host of the entertainment show "Access Hollywood," but will keep a role on the morning program.
NBC said Wednesday, May 4, 2016, that it hasn't been determined whether she will continue to host the third hour from California or if that role will go to someone else.
(Photo by Paul A. Hebert/Invision/AP, File)
